\f0\b Support:
\f1\b0 \
\
There are several sources of support that you will find useful. Please take a few moments to read the various text documents that come with this distribution of PreceptorTools.  These documents contain information that can speed up your learning.  The PreceptorTools palette that is launched every time you load a PreceptorTools module has quite a bit of application related information available at the click of a button. Access this by clicking the "Help" button at the bottom of the PreceptorTools palette. Finally, if you have an internet connection, you can connect directly to the PreceptorTools online reference hosted by Messimer Computing, Inc. This set of pages is the definitive resource for PreceptorTools.  There are two ways to get there: 1) type "http://www.messimercomputing.com/pToolsRef.html" into your internet browser or click the "window to the world" icon located in the title bar of the PreceptorTools "Help" window.\
